ArcelorMittal S. Africa to Raise Hot-Rolled Coil 3.5%

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-03-04T11:00:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-02/arcelormittal-south-africa-to-raise-hot-rolled-coil-price-3-5-from-april.html
(Corrects to specify specialty price in second paragraph in
story originally published March 2.)    ArcelorMittal South Africa Ltd. (ACL)  will
raise its hot-rolled coil price by 3.5 percent for deliveries
from April 1.  The benchmark specialty long-steel product price will
increase 4.9 percent, the Johannesburg-based company said in an
e-mailed response to a query today. Plate prices will rise 3.1
percent and cold-rolled coil 3.1 percent, the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  